import React from 'react'
import { Navbar, Nav, Container, NavDropdown } from 'react-bootstrap'
import { LinkContainer} from "react-router-dom"

const Header = () => {
    return (
        <header>
            <Navbar variant="dark" expand="lg" collapseOnSelect>
                <Container>
                    <LinkContainer to="/">
                        ManageMe
                    </LinkContainer>
                    
                </Container>
            </Navbar>
        </header>
    )
}

export default Header
